{"prompt": "Develop a comprehensive portal for a government consulting group. The primary color should be a deep hunter green.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Government Consulting Group</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #014421; /* Deep Hunter Green */\n            --secondary-color: #4F7942; /* A slightly lighter, less contrasting green */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n            --hover-color: #2E8B57; /* Sea Green for hover effects */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); /* Slightly transparent white for sections */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(1, 68, 33, 0.7), rgba(1, 68, 33, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/014421/ffffff?text=Government+Consulting') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            min-height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .service-list {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            flex-basis: calc(33% - 20px);\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        #about, #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about .container {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        #about .text-content {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        #about .image-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .service-item {\n                flex-basis: 100%;\n            }\n            #about .container {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            #about .image-content {\n                margin-top: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Government Consulting Group</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Driving Excellence in Public Service</h2>\n            <p>Dedicated to providing strategic insights and innovative solutions for government agencies.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-list\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Developing data-driven strategies to achieve organizational goals and enhance public impact.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-cog\"></i>\n                    <h3>Operational Efficiency</h3>\n                    <p>Optimizing processes and resource allocation for improved government operations.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Program Management</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance in managing complex public sector programs from inception to completion.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Policy Analysis</h3>\n                    <p>In-depth analysis of policies and their implications for governmental bodies.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Innovation & Technology</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging technology and innovative approaches to modernize public services.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Stakeholder Engagement</h3>\n                    <p>Facilitating effective communication and collaboration with diverse stakeholders.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"text-content\">\n                <h2>About Our Firm</h2>\n                <p>We are a team of dedicated professionals with extensive experience in public administration, policy development, and operational management. Our mission is to empower government entities with the knowledge and tools necessary to serve their communities effectively and efficiently. We pride ourselves on our integrity, our commitment to results, and our deep understanding of the public sector's unique challenges and opportunities.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"image-content\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/4F7942/ffffff?text=Our+Team\" alt=\"Our Team\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Government Consulting Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent successfully!');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}